.SH NAME
TextMetrics.ideographicBaseline \- TextMetrics: ideographicBaseline
property
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[B]Note:\f[R] This feature is available in Web Workers.
.PP
The read\-only \f[CR]ideographicBaseline\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]TextMetrics\f[R] interface is a \f[CR]double\f[R] giving the
distance from the horizontal line indicated by the
\f[CR]CanvasRenderingContext2D.textBaseline\f[R] property to the
ideographic baseline of the line box, in CSS pixels.
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP
.EX
\f[B]const\f[R] canvas = document.createElement(\[dq]canvas\[dq]);
\f[B]const\f[R] ctx = canvas.getContext(\[dq]2d\[dq]);
\f[B]const\f[R] text = ctx.measureText(\[dq]foo\[dq]); \f[I]// returns TextMetrics object\f[R]

text.ideographicBaseline; \f[I]// \-1.201171875;\f[R]
